{"tid":2492612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國第一狗仔隊卓偉公布訪問指　曾志偉及鄧光榮性侵藍潔瑛　　曾志偉發聲明否認","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T18:31:08.000Z","uid":204533,"like":114,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"939e40c5453e53dc5765eee0e8ad63db48fa0edc","tid":2492612,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"2013年12月，藍潔瑛接受香港雜誌《Next Magazine》專訪時透露，自己早年遭到兩位影壇大哥性侵，雖然受訪時有提及兩位影壇大哥姓名，但此錄音遭錄製刪除。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>2018年1月「中國第一狗仔」卓偉在微博上揭露未經剪接過藍潔瑛訪談內容，影片顯示曾志偉和鄧光榮為藍潔瑛的性侵者。</strong></span></span>隨後曾志偉發表聲明否認，指影片經過後製剪接，並非為原影片，曾志偉委任律師揚言喊告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2600643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2600643&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=2714d90f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2600643&h=95c3a1a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2600643</a><br />\n<br />\n點睇？<br />\n<br />\n你覺得卓偉講既係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾志偉先係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a2fb73d4e6fefdc2e20439ccd42966a0d6b057","tid":2492612,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmeh11dDdicj2DSC7Sm7eRJJT62DKGpf5B12du6MRrxuNM?filename=GjZ998k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjZ998k.jpg&h=4c83e5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWusYKNhgLZV6z2adMbXhi48J2nvyjcFZumVSQibnn49M?filename=NshcosY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNshcosY.jpg&h=9c61a42c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42050f4543a25f6556ef9bc6c6f06ca1f326623a","tid":2492612,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":